theorem Topology.frontier_eq_univ_of_dense_and_interior_empty
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} (hDense : Dense A)
    (hInt : interior A = (∅ : Set X)) :
    frontier A = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  calc
    frontier A = closure A \ interior A := by
      simp [frontier]
    _ = (Set.univ : Set X) \ (∅ : Set X) := by
      simpa [hDense.closure_eq, hInt]
    _ = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
      simp
